{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c6b1d8cd73","title":"普察英野战军有配合东北作战的任务","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"557cf7ef51","index":0,"year":1948,"month":4,"day":22,"articleId":"c6b1d8cd73"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji24.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji24":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e6e77066db","type":"paragraph","text":"普察英野战军有配合东北作战的任务“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c6b1d8cd73"},{"id":"749bbb89a7","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年4月22日）杨、罗、杨、耿你们有配合东北作战的任务，主力三个纵队必须于辰初出动，辰删以前到达热河境内。因此，你们派赴门头沟之一个级队应立即收回，集结三个级队于桑干河以南休息至展冬左右为止，准备七天携根并在政治上完成远出之一切准备工作，注意不要暴露企图待命出动。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c6b1d8cd73"},{"id":"000c34b928","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c6b1d8cd73"},{"id":"740d880f72","type":"paragraph","text":"卵养玄口]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给看察我野战军司令员杨得志、2热河，旧省名，辖今河北省东北部、辽宁省西南部和内蒙古自治区[3]门头沟，今为北京市的一个区。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c6b1d8cd73"}],"page":{"id":"78384ce00d","publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c6b1d8cd73","start":230,"end":230}}}},"__N_SSG":true}